                            <comment id="13485238" author="revans2" created="Fri, 26 Oct 2012 22:06:04 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This can save several hundred MB on an AM with many reduce tasks.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13486256" author="revans2" created="Mon, 29 Oct 2012 18:59:15 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;There are no tests for this patch.  I have tested it manually.  All of the old functionality should still work, it is just that more memory will be released to be collected when a call finishes.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
